summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from Charles W. Brassington and Louise H. Brassington, his wife; Katherine Mary Siegle and husband, Albert C.; Walter A. Bowles; Sarah L. Edmunds and Frederick J. Edmunds, her husband; Letitia Louise Anderson; and James McRobert and Addie A. McRobert, his wife; to the City of Seattle and laying off Seaview Terrace.
